🧠 MindForge - Smart Study Planner
MindForge is a sleek, beginner-friendly productivity web app designed for students to manage their subjects, track their academic progress, and stay motivated with daily quotes and deadlines — all in a stylish card interface.

PROJECT STRUCTURE 
📁 MindForge/
├── index.html            → Main HTML structure
├── styles.css            → Responsive and modern styling
├── js/
│   ├── app.js            → Subject, quote, dark mode, deadline logic
│   ├── progress.js       → Progress tracker slider functionality
│   ├── tt.js             → Real-time timetable highlighting
└── images/               → GitHub and LinkedIn icons

✨ Features
✅ Add subjects dynamically

📊 Visual progress tracker with interactive sliders

🗓️ Weekly timetable with real-time day/time highlight

💡 Daily motivational quotes (auto + refresh)

📌 Upcoming deadlines list (auto populated)

🌙 Toggle between light and dark mode

🧾 Fully responsive card-based layout

👨‍💻 Footer with social links

🧪 How to Run
Download or clone this repo

Open index.html in any modern browser

Start managing your studies 💪

No backend or dependencies needed. It's a pure HTML + CSS + JS frontend project.

